# Sri Lanka Dengue Cases 2010 - 2020
##  **About The Data**
- Data scraped from a government website ([Click Here]( https://www.epid.gov.lk/))
- Dataset Include time series data about Sri Lanka recorded dengue cases from 2010 to 2020 with district wise separation 
- There Are three features (columns) : 1)Date , 2) City , 3) value (Number Of Dengue Cases)

       1) Date : Describe the year & month

       2) City : Corresponding City

       3) Value : Number of recorded dengue cases

- Used this data for my project about *Sri Lanka Dengue Status Evaluation & Visualization* then I decided to publish this on Kaggle because I believe this will help to gain new knowledge. here I attached the link for that.
[Sri Lanka Dengue Status Evaluation & Visualization](https://github.com/Nsadaa/Sri-Lanka-Dengue-Status-Evaluation-Visualization)

##  **License**
- All the data data scraped from above Sri Lanka's government website therefore all the credit goes to the first owners & do not change the data
- Use this only for educational purposes ( Don't use for any commercial purposes )
